OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Most people do not believe workers will
OL,6, return to the office full-time after   
OL,7, the coronavirus pandemic, an exclusive 
OL,8, survey for the BBC suggests.           
OL,10,FA total of 70% of 1,684 people polled  
OL,11,Fpredicted that workers would "never    
OL,12,Freturn to offices at the same rate".   
OL,14,FThe majority of workers said that they 
OL,15,Fwould prefer to work from home either  
OL,16,Ffull-time or at least some of the time.
OL,18,FBut managers raised concerns that      
OL,19,Fcreativity in the workplace would be   
OL,20,Faffected.                              
